SUMMARY:Homeschool Learning Lab
DESCRIPTION:Homeschool Learning Lab is a weekly program that offers 
 engaging enrichment lessons created just for homeschoolers. Come join us 
 each week to learn\, explore\, and connect with other homeschooling 
 families in Durham!\n\nIf you have any questions\, accessibility questions 
 or accommodation needs\, please contact Molly at mschaefer@dconc.gov.  We 
 ask that all requests be made at least three (3) business days prior to the 
 event to ensure we can provide the best accommodations possible!
LOCATION:North Regional Library (221 Milton Rd)
ORGANIZER;CN="Molly Schaefer":MAILTO:mschaefer@dconc.gov
CATEGORIES:Homeschool
UID:LibCal-14288-16136897
