SUMMARY:This Week In the Lab: Makey Makeys
DESCRIPTION:Join the Maker   STEAM Team in the Innovation Lab during 
 specified open hours to discover how you can use the properties of 
 electricity and circuit building in order to create a game controller with 
 a Makey Makey kit! \n\nThis is a self-paced activity. You can drop in 
 during the listed Open Lab Hours.\n\nInnovation Lab Open Hours:\n\nMonday: 
 Closed\nTuesday: 1pm - 5pm\nWednesday: closed (*different this 
 week)\nThursday: 10am - 2pm\nFriday: 1pm - 5pm\nSaturday: 11am - 1pm and 
 3pm - 5pm\n\nHours subject to change based on staffing and programming 
 needs.
LOCATION:Main Library (300 N. Roxboro St)
ORGANIZER;CN="Caroline Flory":MAILTO:cflory@dconc.gov
CATEGORIES:Arts & Crafts, Maker, STEAM
UID:LibCal-14288-16025490
URL:https://durhamcountylibrary.libcal.com/event/16025490
