SUMMARY:Storytime with Ms. Chloe
DESCRIPTION:Come join us in the Children's Programming Room for Storytime 
 with Ms. Chloe. This is a noisy Storytime that will be full of reading\, 
 singing\, dancing\, rhythm sticks\, and bubbles! \n\nAfterwards we will 
 play with dinosaurs and coloring pages.\n\nGeared towards toddlers to 
 Kindergarteners\, but all ages are welcome to join in the fun!\n\nChildren 
 under the age of 10 must be supervised by an adult.\n\nFor more 
 information\, contact: chloebullock@dconc.gov\n
