SUMMARY:Bookmobile Stop: Carolina Arbors
DESCRIPTION:Our library-on-wheels serves local neighborhoods\, shopping 
 centers\, and other community locations. We're open to all so check out our 
 schedule to visit any of our many stops throughout Durham County. We have 
 titles for children\, teens\, and adults\, in both English and Spanish. See 
 our full bookmobile schedule here. \n\n*This schedule is subject to change 
 without notice due to weather\, traffic\, or mechanical difficulties.
LOCATION:Bookmobile\, Offsite
