SUMMARY:Memory Cafe
DESCRIPTION:Come join us for a monthly activity for people with dementia 
 and their caregivers. Memory Cafes host activities designed to engage in 
 the present\, without the expectations of using short-term memory or 
 forward thinking. This month\, we will celebrate our loved ones with a 
 Valentine's Party! Come enjoy music\, snacks\, and Valentine's candy\, of 
 course! \n\nIf you have any accessibility questions or accommodation 
 needs\, please contact me at dpeterson@dconc.gov. We ask that all requests 
