SUMMARY:Nutrition Workshop: 3 Steps to Simple & Balanced Meal Planning
DESCRIPTION:Take the guess work out of healthy eating by joining our free\, 
 nutrition workshop! In 3 Steps to Healthy & Balanced Meal Planning\, 
 participants will:\n\n\n	\n	Learn how to plan a week of simple 
 meals.\n	\n	\n	Practice building meals using everyday\, affordable 
 foods.\n	\n	\n	Learn how to set-up their kitchen for ease and more 
 efficiency. \n	\n	\n	Learn how to adapt meals for busy schedules\, 
 preferences\, or household needs.\n	\n	\n	Reduce overwhelm and decision 
 fatigue around the question: “what's for dinner?”\n	\n\n\nThis workshop 
 is presented by Lucy Hayhurst\, founder of Well Balanced Nutrition. As a 
 licensed and registered dietician\, Lucy has over a decade's worth of 
 experience in nutrition counseling and wellness coaching.\n\nRegistration 
 is required.
LOCATION:Meeting Room #4311\, Main Library (300 N. Roxboro St)
ORGANIZER;CN="Austin Daniels":MAILTO:ausdaniels@dconc.gov
CATEGORIES:Business, Food & Cooking, Health & Fitness
