 genres. Each meeting\, we will discuss the craft of writing and review each 
 other's works. To submit an item for critique\, email dpeterson@dconc.gov 
 by January 29. Registered attendees will receive works to review on January 
 30. Email dpeterson@dconc.gov with questions or to register after 
