SUMMARY:North Durham Chess Club
DESCRIPTION:Participate in the Royal Game of Chess!  \n\nThe North Durham 
 Library Chess Club will meet on the second Saturday of every month from 
 1:30-5:30 pm.  All are welcome to attend regardless of age or skill level. 
 Instruction will be provided to beginners and novices. Sets and boards are 
 provided\, but you are welcome to bring your own if you wish.  Attendance 
 is free\; no registration needed.\n\n \n\n \n\n\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n 
 \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nQuestions? Call North Regional Library at 
 919-560-0236 or email the North Durham Chess Club at 
 pnousak@mindspring.com.
