DESCRIPTION:The Bookmobile will be at the Scrap Exchange on Saturday from 
 3:00 - 5:00pm. Visit the Bookmobile and complete a small craft. No 
 registration required!\n\nThe Scrap Exchange\n\n2050 Chapel Hill Rd\, 
 Durham\, 27707\n\nInformation about our Bookmobile: \n\nOur 
 library-on-wheels serves local neighborhoods\, shopping centers\, and other 
 community locations. We're open to all so check out our schedule to visit 
 any of our many stops throughout Durham County. We have titles for 
 children\, teens\, and adults\, in both English and Spanish. See our full 
 bookmobile schedule here. \n\n*This schedule is subject to change without 
 notice due to weather\, traffic\, or mechanical difficulties.
