SUMMARY:Valentine's Day Sensory Bottles
DESCRIPTION:At this Valentine’s Day Sensory Bottle program\, children 
 will create their own festive sensory bottles using colorful materials like 
 glitter\, beads\, and Valentine-themed items. This calming\, creative 
 activity supports fine motor skills and sensory exploration while giving 
 kids a special keepsake to take home. Perfect for little hands and big 
 imaginations!\n\nIf you have any accessibility questions or accommodation 
 needs\, please contact us at cromero@dconc.gov. We ask that all requests be 
 made at least three (3) business days prior to the event to ensure we can 
 provide the best accommodations possible! All ages are welcome! PLEASE ONLY 
 REGISTER YOUR CHILD/CHILDREN!
