DESCRIPTION:Love to knit\, crochet\, or do other handiwork? Just getting 
 started and looking for some tips from an experienced knitter or crocheter? 
 Bring your project and your questions and join us at the library! This 
 fun\, mostly social gathering is a great time for showing off your latest 
