SUMMARY:ESOL Intermediate Level Class
DESCRIPTION:***MAIN LIBRARY REGISTRATION IS CLOSED*** Students should take 
 placement test with the Durham Literacy Center before attending classes. 
 Classes will start on Monday\, February 9 with the semester ending on 
 Wednesday\, May 13. Classes will be held on Monday/Wednesday from 10:00 
 a.m. - 12:00 p.m. in Conference Room #3214 at Main Library. If you would 
 like more information about the registration process or have questions\, 
 please email ESOL@durhamliteracy.org or call the ESOL Program by phone at 
