BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20260217T230000Z
DTEND:20260218T003000Z
DTSTAMP:20260217T000000Z
SUMMARY:Durham Business Listening Tour
DESCRIPTION:Give It To The People® x Commissioner Michelle Burton x Durham 
 County Library SBC\n\nAs one of the NC’s leading curators of business 
 education\, professional development\, and ecosystem-building experiences\, 
 Give It To The People® knows that sustainable growth starts with real 
 conversations. This tour is designed to meet business owners where they 
 are\, understand the challenges they face\, and identify how they’re 
 accessing (or struggling to access) the resources available across Durham 
 and the Triangle.\n\nCommissioner Michelle Burton brings the heart of an 
 educator and the vision of a public servant to this initiative. Together\, 
 we are committed to being intentional about listening\, truly listening\, 
 to what Durham’s business community needs to grow\, hire\, scale\, 
 innovate\, and stay competitive.\n\nEvery stop on the tour will create 
 space for entrepreneurs to share their lived experiences\, offer insight on 
 what’s working and what isn’t\, and shape future solutions that reflect 
 the real needs of our community. From new startups to established firms\, 
 from solo consultants to brick-and-mortar owners\, this tour is a chance to 
 ensure Durham’s economic ecosystem is responsive\, equitable\, and built 
 to last.\n\nAs an added benefit\, every attendee will have the opportunity 
 to join the Give It Get It Biz Membership\, the premier hub for small 
 business connectivity\, training\, events\, and ecosystem access in Durham. 
 Membership opens the door to resources\, relationships\, and opportunities 
 that help entrepreneurs navigate the region more effectively and stay 
 plugged into the support system they deserve.\n\nThis Listening Tour is a 
 commitment to building a stronger\, more connected Durham where business 
 owners feel seen\, supported\, and equipped to thrive.\n\nLet’s Give It & 
  Get It Together. REGISTER HERE: Durham Business Listening Tour by Give It 
 To The People
LOCATION:SLW Meeting Room - Full Room\, Stanford L. Warren Branch Library (1201 Fayetteville St)
ORGANIZER;CN="Ciera Williams":MAILTO:cbwilliams@dconc.gov
CATEGORIES:
UID:LibCal-14288-15965816
URL:https://durhamcountylibrary.libcal.com/event/15965816
END:VEVENT
