SUMMARY:Family Storytime @ Southwest Regional
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a Saturday morning Family Storytime that will 
 include stories\, fingerplays and interactive songs!\n\nDrop in and join 
 us\, no registration is required! All ages welcome.\n\n \n\nIf you have 
 questions about accessibility\, program stimulation levels\, and/or need 
 disability accommodations\, please contact us at (919) 560-8592. \n\n\n
LOCATION:Southwest Meeting Room\, Southwest Regional Library (3605 Shannon Rd)
ORGANIZER;CN="Kristen Stockdale":MAILTO:kstockdale@dconc.gov
