SUMMARY:Downtown Durham Chess Club
DESCRIPTION:\n\nParticipate in the Royal Game of Chess! \n\nThe Downtown 
 Durham Chess Club meets on selected Saturdays from 1:30-5:30 pm\; check the 
 calendar for dates.  All are welcome to attend regardless of age or skill 
