SUMMARY:Black History Month Scavenger Hunt at Southwest Regional
DESCRIPTION:February is Black History Month\, and February 2026 marks a 
 century (100 years) of national commemorations of Black history! 
 \n\nWe’ve hidden 10 pictures of recently published biographies on Black 
 figures of the past and present who have made incredible contributions to 
 society. Can you find them all? Stop by the Kids Desk to get started!
