SUMMARY:Tabletop Troupe - Board Games\, Card Games\, & TTRPGs
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to Tabletop Troupe!\n\nThis is a club for ages 7-14 who 
 like all things board games\, card games\, and TTRPGs.\n\nEach meeting\, 
 we'll be learning how to play a new game\, and we will have open games for 
 anyone to walk in and play.\n\nThis February\, we'll be focusing on 
 learning the board game ROOT!\n\nRegistration is optional.\n\nFeedback 
 Form\n\n \n\nThis program is made possible by a donation from the Friends 
 of the Durham Library. \n\nNew games were purchased through Guildhall 
 Games\, a local game & toy store in Boxyard RTP committed to providing a 
 safe and welcoming space for underrepresented communities in the area.
