SUMMARY:Road to Wealth Series: Estate Planning
DESCRIPTION:Hosted by Habitat for Humanity of Durham and presented by The 
 Law Offices of Steven A. Drake and Vincent Boone\, a licensed State Farm 
 Agent. This program will explain the fundamentals of insurance\, how it 
 works\, and the protections it offers. Additionally\, participants will 
 learn the key stages of estate planning as they relate to insurance 
 decisions. \n\n*Please Note*\n\nThis program is for educational purposes 
 only. No legal services or legal advice will be provided\n\nFor more 
 information please contact Homeowner Services at Habitat for Humanity of 
 Durham at homeownerservices@durhamhabitat.org.
LOCATION:Southwest Meeting Room\, Southwest Regional Library (3605 Shannon Rd)
ORGANIZER;CN="Jason Howard":MAILTO:jchoward@dconc.gov
CATEGORIES:Finance
