DESCRIPTION:Are you a fan of comic books or graphic novels? Join us on ZOOM 
 for this month's meeting of Durham County Library's Graphic Book 
 Club.\n\nEach month we pick a type of story (fantasy\, crime\, manga\, 
 etc)\, then come together to talk about our books and share our ideas and 
 impressions of what we read.\n\nOur topic this month: To be 
 determined!\n\nJoin us on Meetup.com for more details about this month's 
 topic\, including springboard/discussion questions and a list of suggested 
 titles.
