SUMMARY:Big Kid Storytime
DESCRIPTION:Geared toward kids and tweens\, ages 7-12! Join us every 
 Tuesday evening for the next chapter in our selected chapter book reading! 
 A snack will be served.\n\nListening to books has serious benefits for 
 developing readers. It helps tweens improve their pronunciation and 
 fluency\, improves focus and memory\, increases attention span\, builds 
 comprehension skills\, and can boost mental health by relieving stress and 
 calming thoughts. \n\n \n\n \n\n
