SUMMARY:Let's Learn Together: Figure Drawing Practice
DESCRIPTION:For February\, we'll be practicing what we learned in our 
 figure drawing classes. We'll split the time drawing from photographs and 
 drawing each other\, so bring (or email me) a photograph and come prepared 
 to model. We'll gather at the beginning and the end to show off what we've 
 done and discuss where we struggled and where we succeeded. \n\nBring your 
 sketchbook and supplies\, if you have them. But if you do not\, all 
 supplies can be provided. Email dpeterson@dconc.gov to reserve supplies or 
 with questions.\n\nThis program is sponsored by the Friends of the Durham 
 Library.
