SUMMARY:Romance Lovers Book Club-The Princess and the PI and And Then There Was the One
DESCRIPTION:All things romance!\n\nThis book club talks about all things 
 romance\, starting with the month's theme but quickly branching out into 
 other books we've been reading and loving\, books we want to read\, and 
 what's going on in Romancelandia - you'll walk away every month with lots 
 of recs for your TBR! Because of our wide-ranging discussions\, you should 
 always feel free to drop in even if you haven't gotten a chance to try the 
 book club picks. This month we're reading\, The Princess and the PI by 
 Nikki Payne And Then There Was the One by Martha Waters. If you want to 
 attend this virtual event\, please register or contact Chelsea Romero at 
 cromero@dconc.gov with any questions.
LOCATION:North Regional Library (221 Milton Rd)
ORGANIZER;CN="Chelsea Romero":MAILTO:cromero@dconc.gov
