DTSTART:20260226T210000Z
DTEND:20260226T223000Z
DTSTAMP:20260226T000000Z
SUMMARY:Pokemon Day
DESCRIPTION:Trainers of all ages are invited to celebrate the world of 
 Pokémon with crafts and activities inspired by your favorite Pokemon! Come 
 and create your own Pokeball with perler beads\, paint your Pokemon designs 
 on rocks\, and trade cards with fellow Pokemon lovers! All materials are 
 provided while supplies are limited.\n\n.
LOCATION:MakerLab\, Main Library (300 N. Roxboro St)
ORGANIZER;CN="Dahlia Bullock":MAILTO:dahbullock@dconc.gov
CATEGORIES:
UID:LibCal-14288-15944676
URL:https://durhamcountylibrary.libcal.com/event/15944676
