SUMMARY:Restorative Yoga
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a 50-minute class for adults that will provide an 
 opportunity for you to relax through gentle stretching and mindful 
 breathing. This class is designed for anyone who would like to slow down\, 
 connect with the body and calm the mind. Both beginners and experienced 
 yogis are welcome. During the class\, you will be guided through a series 
 of yoga poses and mindful breathing techniques intended to calm the busy 
 mind and stretch the body. Registration is required. \n\nPlease provide 
 your own mat or a towel.\n\nIf you have questions about accessibility\, 
 program stimulation levels\, and/or need disability accommodations\, please 
 contact us at 919-560-7192.
