SUMMARY:Spanish U Intermediate Class
DESCRIPTION:This session is currently full. We’ve added this new date to 
 accommodate the session that was postponed due to inclement weather on 
 January 24.\n\n\nAre you ready to start learning Spanish in the new 
 year?\n\nJoin us at the Main Library for Spanish U\, a free 5-week course 
 designed for intermediate-level adult learners\, global citizens\, and 
 lifelong learners! Classes begin Saturday\, January 24 and include a 
 complimentary workbook.\n\nRegistration is required and opens on Saturday\, 
 December 27 - save the date!\n\nThis program is made possible through a 
 generous grant from the Durham Library Foundation.
