BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20260302T200000Z
DTEND:20260302T204500Z
DTSTAMP:20260302T000000Z
SUMMARY:Crazy 8s Club - Glow-in-the-Dark Geometry (Math for K thru 3)
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to Crazy 8s Math Club!\n\nKids need to catch up on 
 math\, so let’s make our after-school time count! \n\nUnlike competitive 
 clubs that appeal to a select few\, Crazy 8s activities – like 
 Glow-in-the-Dark Geometry and Beach Ball Party – are designed for kids of 
 all math abilities. Join Dilip Barman\, for activities that teach 
 foundational math skills. Each week will cover different topics\, so be 
 sure to register for all the events in the series. \n\nWeek 
 1\n\nGlow-in-the-Dark Geometry \n\nGlowsticks bring repeating patterns and 
 3D shapes to life in kids’ hands!\n\nMath Skills: 2-D geometric shapes\; 
 Counting\; Pattern recognition\; Building a cube\n\n \n\nWeek 2\n\nBeach 
 Ball Party \n\nForget flash cards. Master math facts with our numbered 
 beach ball!\n\nMath Skills: Addition and subtraction\; Comparison of 
 numbers\; Logic: thinking ahead multiple steps\n\n \n\nWeek 3\n\nBouncy 
 Dice Explosion\n\nRoll the dice and do the math to capture the winning 
 Bingo square!\n\nMath Skills: Addition\; Counting\; Frequency\; 
 Subtraction\, Strategic thinking\n\n \n\nWeek 4\n\nCrazy 8s Race\n\nTeams 
 speed around a figure 8 racetrack to be the first to 8 x 8!\n\nMath Skills: 
 Addition\; Introduction to the concept of multiples of 8\; Number 
 recognition\n\n \n\nWeek 5\n\nPixel-palooza\n\nCreate giant\, pixelated 
 pictures out of sticky notes to explore addition\, subtraction and the 
 distributive property!\n\nMath Skills: Area and perimeter\; Fractions and 
 proportions\; Graphing\; Addition\; Subtraction\; Scale\n\n \n\nWeek 
 6\n\nDaring Darts\n\nSupersize the math fun in this game of floor 
 darts!\n\nMath Skills: Addition\; Number recognition\; Number value 
 comparison\; Subtraction\n\n \n\nWeek 7\n\nFunny Money\n\nIt’s payday! 
 Compare coins\, race to earn money\, then go shopping for a cool 
 puzzle.\n\nMath Skills: Addition\; Basic financial literacy\; Skip 
 counting\; Valuing\, comparing units of money\n\n \n\nWeek 8\n\nSpy 
 Training\n\nSolve math-y codes for clues to unlock the hidden spy 
 gear!\n\nMath Skills: Association between sets\; Adding\; Subtracting\; 
 Number recognition\; Pattern recognition
LOCATION:South Regional - Children's Programming Room\, South Regional Library (4505 S. Alston Ave)
ORGANIZER;CN="Amaris Torres":MAILTO:amaristorres@dconc.gov
CATEGORIES:Arts & Crafts, Social, STEAM
UID:LibCal-14288-16210232
URL:https://durhamcountylibrary.libcal.com/calendar/14288/crazy8s
END:VEVENT
