SUMMARY:March Federal Primary and Election
DESCRIPTION:Durham County will be conducting the Statewide Primary and 
 Election on Tuesday\, March 3\, 2026\, and the Statewide General Election 
 on Tuesday\, November 3\, 2026. Registered voters will be permitted to vote 
 either by mail\, in-person at an early voting site\, or in-person at their 
 assigned Election Day polling place. \n\n \n\nOn Election Day\, be sure to 
 go to your assigned precinct's polling place. Use the North Carolina State 
 Board of Elections' Polling Place Lookup Tool to ensure you go to the 
 correct polling place.\n\nTell us about your voting experience by 
 completing our survey below!\n\nElection Day Voter Experience Survey
