SUMMARY:Morning Crochet
DESCRIPTION:Get hooked on crochet with your neighbors at the morning 
 Crochet Club!\n\nLove to crochet? Just getting started\, and looking for 
 some tips from an experienced crocheter? \n\nBring your project and your 
 questions and join us the second and fourth Tuesdays in the 
 library.\n\nThis fun\, mostly social gathering is a great time for showing 
 off your latest creation\, getting inspiration for your next one\, or 
 seeking help when you've hit a crochet roadblock.\n\nQuestions? Call the 
