SUMMARY:This Week In the Lab: Ozobots
DESCRIPTION:Join the Maker   STEAM Team in the Innovation Lab during 
 specified open hours to discover the power of robotics thorugh color! Code 
 our special color sensing Ozobots by drawing directly onto the page\, or 
 dive deep into the basics of block coding using the Ozoblockly 
 software!\n\nThis is a self-paced activity. You can drop in during the 
 listed Open Lab Hours.\n\nInnovation Lab Open Hours:\n\nMonday: 
 Closed\nTuesday: 1pm - 5pm\nWednesday: 3pm - 6pm (*different this 
 week)\nThursday: 10am - 2pm\nFriday: 1pm - 5pm\nSaturday: 11am - 1pm and 
 3pm - 5pm\n\nHours subject to change based on staffing and programming 
 needs.
LOCATION:Main Library (300 N. Roxboro St)
ORGANIZER;CN="Caroline Flory":MAILTO:cflory@dconc.gov
