SUMMARY:Tabletop Troupe - Board\, Card\, & TTRPG Club
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to Tabletop Troupe! \n\nThis is a club for ages 7-14 
 who like all things board games\, card games\, and TTRPGs.\n\nEach 
 meeting\, we'll be learning how to play a new game\, and we will have open 
 games for anyone to walk in and play.\n\nThis January\, we'll be focusing 
 on learning Exploding Kittens!\n\nRegistration is optional.\n\n \n\nThis 
 program is made possible by a donation from the Friends of the Durham 
 Library. \n\nNew games were purchased through Guildhall Games\, a local 
 game & toy store in Boxyard RTP committed to providing a safe and welcoming 
 space for underrepresented communities in the area.
