SUMMARY:Elementary Explorers
DESCRIPTION:During this after-school program kids (ages 5-12) will explore 
 Science\, Technology\, Engineering\, Art\, and Mathematics (STEAM) through 
 fun\, hands-on activities! Every other week we will learn about a new 
 concept\, then do a related project\, experiment\, or game to encourage 
 critical thinking\, creativity\, and collaboration!\n\n3/3/26: 
 Kaleidoscopes!\n\nNo registration is required. Open for all.\n\nQuestions? 
 Please email Lauren at lwise@dconc.gov or call 919-560-0236.  Thank you!
