SUMMARY:Storytime with Ms. Lauren
DESCRIPTION:Please join us for a storytime designed to promote early 
 literacy skills through interactive stories\, songs\, games\, and other fun 
 activities!  While content is geared toward preschoolers (ages 3-5 years)\, 
 all are welcome to join in on the fun! The program runs for about 25 
 minutes\, and families are invited to stay afterward for open play and 
 socialization time. Open for all!\n\nThis program has a mix of sensory 
 elements\, some high energy (e.g. singing and moving) and some low energy 
 (e.g. listening quietly to stories). \n\nIf you have any accessibility 
 questions or accommodation needs\, please email Lauren at lwise@dconc.gov. 
 We ask that all requests be made at least three (3) business days prior to 
 the event to ensure we can provide the best accommodations possible! Thank 
 you!\n
