DTEND:20260305T003000Z
DTSTAMP:20260304T000000Z
SUMMARY:Let's Learn Together: Figure Drawing
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we learn to use Linkedin Learning by signing up for 
 Drawing Foundations: Figure. We will learn how to access Linkedin Learning 
 and sign up for the class so participants can rewatch the videos at home. 
 Each week\, we will watch a different lesson and put it into practice as we 
 learn to draw the human figure\n\nRegistration is required. Registration 
 for the first session will automatically register you for all sessions 
 through March. Sketchbooks can be provided but please bring your own 
 drawing supplies as well (sketchbook\, pencils\, erasers.) Email 
 dpeterson@dconc.gov with questions or accommodation requests.
LOCATION:North Regional - Children's Programming Room\, North Regional Library (221 Milton Rd)
ORGANIZER;CN="Desiree Peterson":MAILTO:dpeterson@dconc.gov
CATEGORIES:Arts & Crafts
