DTSTAMP:20260304T000000Z
SUMMARY:Forever Young Book Club
DESCRIPTION:A book club for adults who read Young Adult. We meet the 1st 
 Wednesday of the month at Boxyard RTP. Grab a glass a wine\, a beer\, or 
 food while we discuss that month's book pick. Haven't read the book? That's 
 okay! Join us for a lively discussion about YA books. The book club meets 
 outside\, so dress for the weather. Questions? Contact Sara Gibson | Family 
 Literacy & Community Services Manager | sgibson@dconc.gov\n\nMarch's Book: 
 Cemetery Boys by Aiden Thomas\n\nBoxyard RTP\n\n900 Park 
 Offices\n\nResearch Triangle Park\, 27709
LOCATION:Offsite
ORGANIZER;CN="Sara Gibson":MAILTO:sgibson@dconc.gov
CATEGORIES:Book Club, Community Engagement
